  "Lista de sites populares por categoria — ROMs (Vimm's, Myrient, CDRomance), patches PT-BR (Tradu-Roms, Romhacking), DLCs (NoPayStation, Hshop). Mesma lista do Windows.": { en: "List of popular sites by category — ROMs (Vimm's, Myrient, CDRomance), PT-BR patches (Tradu-Roms, Romhacking), DLCs (NoPayStation, Hshop). Same list as Windows.", es: "Lista de sitios populares por categoría — ROMs (Vimm's, Myrient, CDRomance), parches PT-BR (Tradu-Roms, Romhacking), DLCs (NoPayStation, Hshop). Misma lista que Windows.", fr: "Liste de sites populaires par catégorie — ROMs (Vimm's, Myrient, CDRomance), patchs PT-BR (Tradu-Roms, Romhacking), DLC (NoPayStation, Hshop). Même liste que Windows.", zh: "按类别列出热门站点——ROM（Vimm's、Myrient、CDRomance）、PT-BR 补丁（Tradu-Roms、Romhacking）、DLC（NoPayStation、Hshop）。与 Windows 列表相同。", ru: "Список популярных сайтов по категориям — ROM (Vimm's, Myrient, CDRomance), патчи PT-BR (Tradu-Roms, Romhacking), DLC (NoPayStation, Hshop). Тот же список, что в Windows." },
