  "Quando ativo, cada perfil tem saves proprios (Yuzu, PCSX2, Dolphin, DuckStation, RPCS3, Project64). Trocar perfil = troca os saves automaticamente. Funciona via junctions Windows (NTFS).": { en: "When active, each profile has its own saves (Yuzu, PCSX2, Dolphin, DuckStation, RPCS3, Project64). Switching profile = switches the saves automatically. Works via Windows junctions (NTFS).", es: "Cuando está activo, cada perfil tiene sus propios saves (Yuzu, PCSX2, Dolphin, DuckStation, RPCS3, Project64). Cambiar de perfil = cambia los saves automáticamente. Funciona mediante junctions de Windows (NTFS).", fr: "Lorsqu'il est actif, chaque profil a ses propres sauvegardes (Yuzu, PCSX2, Dolphin, DuckStation, RPCS3, Project64). Changer de profil = change les sauvegardes automatiquement. Fonctionne via les junctions Windows (NTFS).", zh: "启用后，每个个人资料都有自己的存档（Yuzu、PCSX2、Dolphin、DuckStation、RPCS3、Project64）。切换个人资料 = 自动切换存档。通过 Windows junctions（NTFS）实现。", ru: "Когда активно, у каждого профиля свои сохранения (Yuzu, PCSX2, Dolphin, DuckStation, RPCS3, Project64). Смена профиля = автоматическая смена сохранений. Работает через junction-точки Windows (NTFS)." },
  "RPCS3 (PS3)": { en: "RPCS3 (PS3)", es: "RPCS3 (PS3)", fr: "RPCS3 (PS3)", zh: "RPCS3 (PS3)", ru: "RPCS3 (PS3)" },
